DBAccessTemplate - org.cyy.fw.android.dborm.sqlite中的类
DB Accessing template
Extract some common codes for accessing DB, such as will call SqliteDBFacade#beginTransaction() when begin to access table, will call SQLiteDatabase#setTransactionSuccessful() after accessing successfully, and will call SQLiteDatabase#endTransaction() to end the logic.

DBAutoUpgradeAdapter - org.cyy.fw.android.dborm.sqlite中的接口
The adapter of auto-upgrade tables
It should be implemented by the user's facade if the user want to the framework check the table's alteration and upgrade the tables automatically while DB upgrades, otherwise user must implement the onUpgrade(SQLiteDatabase, int, int) for upgrading logic.
